jobs.name: Chester
jobs.long: The club play at Holt House, which was previously the home ground of Colne Dynamoes.[5] The ground was originally an area with several pitches, before being enclosed in 1975 when Dynamoes joined the Lancashire Combination, although it continued to be used for cricket.[5] Between 1982 and 1985 three stands were erected and floodlights installed.
